        <abstract>
            <para>Brecknock Wildlife Trust (now WTSWW Brecknockshire) species records collated and digitised by BIS. Many are on WTSWW BWT reserves or Wildlife Sites and include general surveys.
Contact BIS for further information or go to website www.bis.org.uk for County recorder contacts.</para>
        </abstract>
