            <qualityControl>
                <description>
                    <para>Records are validated for geographical area on import to BIS database. BIS makes every effort to exchange with county recorders for verification but due to the historical nature of this dataset some records remain unverified. Data will have been collected by local experts, ecological consultants, ecologists and members of the public.</para>
